Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.50,0:01:33.26,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Trouble arises over\Nsuccession rights
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.26,0:01:36.74,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,in one of Soul Society’s high-ranking\Naristocratic families, the Kasumiohji Clan.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.10,0:01:40.68,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Their princess, Rurichiyo Kasumiohji,\Ntraveled to the World of the Living.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.82,0:01:45.45,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo reluctantly agrees to\Nbecome her bodyguard.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.46,0:01:48.50,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Rurichiyo, who is unaware that\Nher life is being targeted,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.54,0:01:52.90,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,turns Ichigo’s life upside down\Nwith her naive behavior.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.90,0:01:55.86,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Elsewhere in the Soul Society,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.90,0:01:59.46,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Shusuke Amagai has become\Nthe new captain of Squad 3
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.46,0:02:01.70,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,and works hard to take on\Nhis new responsibilities.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.82,0:02:05.94,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(362,266)}He went over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.20,0:02:07.05,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Get him!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.62,0:02:15.38,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,We lost him! Which way?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.74,0:02:16.88,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,This way!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.54,0:02:20.95,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry! Don’t lose him!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.18,0:02:42.04,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Stay still.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.75,0:02:52.82,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I got you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.34,0:02:56.79,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Third Seat Kibune.\NGood job!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.09,0:03:00.22,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You’re putting too much effort\Ninto this, Lieutenant Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.58,0:03:02.63,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Lieutenant, please confirm.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.63,0:03:03.94,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.78,0:03:06.21,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}MISSING CAT: MALE -AGE 3
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.01,0:03:11.03,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,No mistake, this is the cat.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.50,0:03:13.16,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Mission complete then.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.16,0:03:17.46,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are we chasing after missing cats\Nfor the aristocrats, anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.46,0:03:20.33,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Yesterday, it was security guards\Nfor a clothing store sale.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.33,0:03:22.71,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Recently, it’s been nothing\Nbut this kind of work.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.05,0:03:26.67,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I’m sure our captain\Nhas his reasons.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.50,0:03:29.42,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think, Lieutenant Kira?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.70,0:03:30.30,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.87,0:03:34.76,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, that’s… I wonder.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.30,0:03:38.48,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I prefer work that I can\Nbe more enthusiastic about.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.48,0:03:39.77,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, now…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.77,0:03:42.27,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,That aside,\Nhow about we go for a drink?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.27,0:03:43.65,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Sounds good.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.65,0:03:44.73,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Let’s go.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.17,0:03:47.22,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,How about you, Lieutenant Kira?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.03,0:03:51.42,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to write up our report.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.34,0:03:58.34,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.13,0:04:02.09,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You’re back, Izuru.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.20,0:04:07.99,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What’s wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.68,0:04:10.43,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,No it’s…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.59,0:04:13.97,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I was a bit startled by\Nbeing called by my first name.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.46,0:04:17.10,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought it would help me\Nfit in with the squad more
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.10,0:04:19.73,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,by calling everyone\Nby their first name.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.13,0:04:21.94,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Don’t like it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.13,0:04:25.91,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh…well…\NIt takes some getting used to.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.91,0:04:28.31,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.03,0:04:31.54,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought it was a good idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.00,0:04:33.88,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Guess I’ll think of something else.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.38,0:04:35.81,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Here is today’s report.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.81,0:04:36.61,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.06,0:04:37.98,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,And…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.62,0:04:42.37,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,About tomorrow’s schedule…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.50,0:04:47.03,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What’s this about doing wall repairs\Nfor the Squad 12 barracks?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.07,0:04:50.26,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Wall repair is just that,\Nrepairing a wall.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.26,0:04:52.90,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,That’s not what I’m trying to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.26,0:04:56.19,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do we have to do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.54,0:04:57.72,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,The others in the squad are also…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.54,0:05:03.74,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Kira, you may not like\Nhearing this, but…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.67,0:05:05.90,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Squad 3 is the one
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.90,0:05:08.52,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,whose previous captain,\NGin Ichimaru, betrayed us.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.83,0:05:09.92,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You understand, don’t you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.16,0:05:16.56,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Once you lose trust,\Nit’s difficult to gain it back.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.25,0:05:21.83,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I don’t know how things will play out,\Nbut it’s better to do this than not.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.02,0:05:25.52,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Relax, Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.50,0:05:31.34,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Seeing you makes me think that\Nthe previous captain, Gin Ichimaru,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.34,0:05:34.78,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,played too big of a role\Nin this squad.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.01,0:05:35.76,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.93,0:05:42.05,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You’re different from Ichimaru.\NNo one expects the same from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.20,0:05:46.17,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Having a charismatic captain is\None way to bring together a team.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.61,0:05:49.34,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,But it can easily break down\Nonce that pillar of support is gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.19,0:05:54.10,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,That’s why I want to re-build a new squad\Ntogether with you and Kibune,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.10,0:05:57.03,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,with the three of us acting as\Nthe pillar of support for this squad.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.50,0:06:02.15,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,So, what happened\Nto Third Seat Kibune?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.58,0:06:03.38,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Well…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.08,0:06:07.04,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}IZAKAYA KAMEGAMEYA
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.66,0:06:06.53,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,He’s drinking with the others.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.27,0:06:08.50,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,After the fight the other day,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.50,0:06:11.97,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Inose and the others seemed to have\Nwarmed up to Third Seat Kibune.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.38,0:06:13.18,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.38,0:06:17.28,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I think I’ll call it a day too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.34,0:06:21.55,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,If something’s bothering you,\Ngo take a break and have some fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.55,0:06:23.22,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Um…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.74,0:06:25.14,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,See you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.62,0:06:29.85,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Have a nice evening, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.46,0:06:37.71,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Today, you’ll be trained in\Na new fighting method.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.70,0:06:42.85,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Recently, there’s been an increase\Nin strong enemies like the Menos.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.46,0:06:45.35,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Such as that Precipice World incident\Nfrom the other day.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.86,0:06:55.53,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,From now on, you must practice
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.53,0:06:58.50,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,working together with\Nyour fellow squad members in battle,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.95,0:07:00.13,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,or else you’ll die.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.34,0:07:06.42,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, this training is to\Nmake sure that doesn’t happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.81,0:07:07.54,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Kibune…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.54,0:07:08.30,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.54,0:07:12.46,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Pick one of these colored headbands.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.38,0:07:15.22,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I’m going to say a color
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.22,0:07:17.05,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,and those wearing that color\Nwill be the enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.96,0:07:21.12,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,The rest of you take on\Nthe enemies in groups of three.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.87,0:07:24.89,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,But, the enemy color\Nwill change periodically.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.50,0:07:29.09,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,The moment I say another color,\Nthe roles will reverse.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.10,0:07:32.55,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,This is to help you develop\Nyour decision-making reflexes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.62,0:07:37.59,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Kibune, you get in the group\Nand lead this exercise.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.97,0:07:38.84,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.99,0:07:40.30,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I will join too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.30,0:07:42.26,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,That’s okay, Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.26,0:07:42.99,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.91,0:07:47.18,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I devised this battle method back\Nwhen I was with the Expedition Unit.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.20,0:07:50.82,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I want Kibune, who’s familiar with\Nthe operation, to lead this training.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.18,0:07:52.10,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.10,0:07:53.07,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.74,0:07:54.34,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Let’s go!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.38,0:07:55.35,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,– Yes, sir!\N– Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.17,0:07:59.79,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,First, purple!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.66,0:08:01.79,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.58,0:08:04.63,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Aida, come with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.00,0:08:05.73,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.73,0:08:09.80,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Inose! Join me in back!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.05,0:08:10.80,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.66,0:08:14.94,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Next, yellow!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.79,0:08:19.08,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Next, red!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.30,0:08:23.85,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Good! Keep it up!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.44,0:08:25.78,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Amazing…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.54,0:08:29.66,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Since when did everyone\Nbecome so organized?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.06,0:08:34.78,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain Amagai’s\Nfighting methods
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.78,0:08:37.79,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,are different from anything\Nwe’ve done before!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.54,0:08:42.43,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain Ichimaru never used\Ngroup fighting methods.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.74,0:08:47.42,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It actually felt like we could put up\Na good fight by working together!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.62,0:08:48.42,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.90,0:08:51.70,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I really like Captain Amagai’s style!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.22,0:08:53.58,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,And Third Seat Kibune too!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.34,0:08:58.12,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,That guy seems more reliable\Nthan Lieutenant Kira!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.50,0:09:01.58,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Soon there might be\Na change in Lieutenants.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.58,0:09:03.15,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Idiot, you’re going too far!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.15,0:09:04.47,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Oops…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.70,0:09:07.70,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Lieutenant Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.90,0:09:08.50,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.90,0:09:10.63,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Third Seat Kibune.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.90,0:09:13.58,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You’re okay…\Nwith what they said just now?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.78,0:09:15.77,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Well…uh…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.30,0:09:18.46,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.05,0:09:22.98,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I must say, Third Seat Kibune,\Nyou’re amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.98,0:09:23.79,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.10,0:09:26.58,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I can’t compare to how you,\NLieutenant Kira,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.58,0:09:28.37,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,have organized\NSquad 3 until now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.37,0:09:29.73,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,That’s not true.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.22,0:09:32.54,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone seems to\Nhave accepted you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.22,0:09:34.47,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,More than me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.47,0:09:35.25,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,But…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.25,0:09:37.23,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s fine!\NDon’t bother with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.90,0:09:44.58,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, sorry. I’m a little tired.\NIf you’ll excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.58,0:10:02.84,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,One more!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.30,0:10:06.43,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You’re a strong drinker, Kira!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.43,0:10:09.10,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, you can have\Nsome of my drink!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.86,0:10:14.43,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You sure can drink.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.86,0:10:16.78,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Say…\NDid something happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.14,0:10:19.68,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.68,0:10:22.92,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Squad 3 is going to\Nchange from now on!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.14,0:10:25.87,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It’ll be different than\Nthe Squad 3 before.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.94,0:10:27.97,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.46,0:10:29.66,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,When the captain changes,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.66,0:10:31.47,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,the atmosphere of\Nthe whole squad changes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.54,0:10:36.62,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I can understand your confusion.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.62,0:10:47.68,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks to Captain Amagai,\NSquad 3’s reputation has improved.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.09,0:10:51.06,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,He’s done good\Nin such a short time.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.42,0:10:54.48,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I…think so to.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.62,0:10:56.39,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Then be proud!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.79,0:11:00.17,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,If you act like this,\Nhow can I put it…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.17,0:11:04.10,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,that new Third Seat guy\Nin Squad 3…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.10,0:11:05.38,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Third Seat Kibune.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.38,0:11:06.62,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.62,0:11:09.58,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,He could take away\Nyour title as Lieutenant!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.94,0:11:11.54,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.46,0:11:16.54,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,That’s right,\NI’m unreliable anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.61,0:11:18.64,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Iba!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.64,0:11:19.92,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Uh… Yeah…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.92,0:11:22.73,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Uh oh,\NI think we touched a nerve.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.34,0:11:24.50,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.50,0:11:25.60,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Party of two, this way!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.60,0:11:26.75,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,– Welcome!\N– Welcome!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.35,0:11:27.88,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have a private room?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.88,0:11:29.88,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, we do!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.26,0:11:33.74,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Speak of the devil.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.74,0:11:36.13,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Why’s he with Captain Kyoraku?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.12,0:11:39.35,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,So, cheers.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.74,0:11:44.98,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I’m happy to have\Nbeen invited for a drink
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.98,0:11:47.95,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,with the new squad captain\Neveryone’s talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.95,0:11:50.55,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I’m still new to this role,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.02,0:11:53.52,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,so getting to know the senior members\Nis also part of my job.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.06,0:11:57.78,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,So, what is it you wanted\Nto talk with me about?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.38,0:12:00.15,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I’ll be straight with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.15,0:12:03.53,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Sounds good.\NI don’t like beating around the bush.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.58,0:12:08.72,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,About the Thirteen Court\NGuard Squads…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.02,0:12:14.31,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Would it be possible for the squads\Nto work more closely together?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.66,0:12:19.45,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,That’s…a difficult subject.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.54,0:12:24.28,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I don’t expect to be able to\Ndo so right away, but at this rate…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.28,0:12:26.48,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, don’t get so excited.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.48,0:12:28.43,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh… I’m sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.66,0:12:31.78,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,But, I like your thinking.\NIt’s not bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.78,0:12:33.40,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You understand!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.70,0:12:37.35,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Amagai, you’re young\Nbut you’re pretty thoughtful.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.35,0:12:39.05,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no! Not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.05,0:12:39.79,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.79,0:12:44.92,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,If we’re talking about these things,\Nmaybe we should talk with Ukitake too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.42,0:12:47.61,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You mean the captain of Squad13?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.78,0:12:52.84,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. This doesn’t mean\NI won’t cooperate.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.84,0:12:56.82,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I just don’t like taking the lead.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.26,0:13:00.58,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,So, next time,\Nlet’s call on Ukitake and talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.58,0:13:01.98,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.98,0:13:03.79,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,By all means!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.06,0:13:07.59,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay! Let’s start again\Nwith a toast!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.14,0:13:10.17,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? You’re not drinking?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.17,0:13:10.92,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,No…I…uh…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.92,0:13:11.58,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.18,0:13:19.56,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.26,0:13:28.29,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hey, hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.54,0:13:32.26,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Don’t tell me…you can’t drink?!\NReally?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.74,0:13:39.62,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Lieutenant Kira, East Area 7,\Nno unusual activity.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.98,0:13:42.23,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Good job, Third Seat Kibune.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.78,0:13:44.86,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,All’s quiet in the inner court.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.86,0:13:45.96,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.98,0:13:48.55,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,That’s good to know.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.58,0:13:55.10,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Is something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.10,0:13:58.12,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, no… It’s nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.38,0:14:04.02,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yes!\NHow about some tea?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.47,0:14:05.62,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Lieutenant Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.62,0:14:07.06,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.18,0:14:10.56,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry for being\Nso rude in asking but,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.18,0:14:14.20,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,why do you always\Nseem so unconfident?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.38,0:14:14.98,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.30,0:14:16.09,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Well…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.78,0:14:18.58,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.47,0:14:27.61,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Urgent message?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.78,0:14:31.58,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,There’s a suspicious shadow\Nnear the execution grounds.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.54,0:14:33.58,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Lieutenant!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.66,0:14:47.35,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Lieutenant! Third Seat!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.35,0:14:49.25,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh… You are…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.54,0:14:50.67,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Shinta Seko.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.94,0:14:53.10,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, I couldn’t\Nremember your name.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.10,0:14:53.84,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,That’s okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.06,0:14:57.23,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I’m still new and\Ndon’t have a seat ranking yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.23,0:14:58.11,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Where did it happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.50,0:14:59.99,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Near this hole.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.34,0:15:03.65,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I saw the suspicious shadow earlier,\Nand tried to go after it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.98,0:15:04.97,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.97,0:15:05.79,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Well…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.10,0:15:09.39,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems to have disappeared\Ninside this hole.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.34,0:15:11.66,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Inside the execution grounds?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.98,0:15:14.09,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing would survive\Nthis fall, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.50,0:15:25.74,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,At this rate…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.30,0:15:36.35,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Lieutenant!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.35,0:15:38.14,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Third Seat Kibune…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.14,0:15:40.35,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.46,0:15:42.54,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I’ll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.54,0:15:43.68,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.10,0:15:46.32,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,But why did\Nthe ground suddenly…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.23,0:15:50.29,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s impossible to climb up.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.54,0:15:53.38,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,There should be\Nan entrance somewhere
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.38,0:15:55.50,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,that brings in\Nthe criminals here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.86,0:15:57.06,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Let’s look for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.06,0:15:57.77,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.39,0:16:02.74,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,This Spiritual Pressure…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.42,0:16:06.34,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,This is…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.58,0:16:11.11,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Why in a place like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.78,0:16:26.22,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,So many…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.98,0:16:29.35,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,But if it’s only this level of Hollow…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.17,0:16:35.23,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.02,0:16:46.08,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Rampage…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.82,0:16:47.82,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Reppu!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.31,0:17:13.75,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Third Seat Kibune…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.54,0:17:22.35,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,This is bad!\NIf the Hollows get outside…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.06,0:17:26.88,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What is he doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.02,0:17:30.84,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Raise your head, Wabisuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.86,0:17:37.97,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing,\NThird Seat Kibune?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.18,0:17:40.44,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Just putting and\Nend to the Hollows.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.62,0:17:42.14,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,But, what about Seko?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.27,0:17:46.61,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,That fool has failed to carry out\Nhis duties as a Soul Reaper.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.74,0:17:50.58,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Falling into enemy hands,\Nand now lying before us in disgrace.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.90,0:17:51.50,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.46,0:17:55.22,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,As one who has taken up\Nthe role of a Soul Reaper,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.22,0:17:56.88,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,he should be prepared\Nto die in battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.86,0:18:02.56,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,By becoming a burden,\Nthis scum has endangered us all.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.98,0:18:04.30,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,He doesn’t deserve to live.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.14,0:18:06.62,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,How could you say such a thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.10,0:18:13.70,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you attempt\Nto save that scum?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.22,0:18:15.74,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You’re too soft!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.74,0:18:16.70,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.50,0:18:19.84,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s that attitude of yours
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.54,0:18:24.15,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,that made you fail to prevent\Nthe former captain’s rebellion beforehand.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.78,0:18:25.78,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn’t that right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.27,0:18:28.29,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,That’s…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.78,0:18:39.83,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.99,0:18:45.80,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It appears you lack\Nthe will as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.13,0:19:08.19,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.34,0:19:12.23,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you guys all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.22,0:19:14.47,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain Amagai…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.58,0:19:20.67,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain! A member was attacked\Nby Hollows and is heavily injured!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.86,0:19:21.85,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait there!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.22,0:19:23.83,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I’ll have the med crew\Nget down there!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.22,0:19:25.08,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.86,0:19:39.91,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain, what about the Hollows\Nthat fled into the sky?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.18,0:19:44.70,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, some squad members nearby\Nsaw it and informed me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.10,0:19:46.53,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,We took care of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.86,0:19:49.15,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that so? Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.86,0:19:52.97,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,We’ve transported Seko\Nto the Squad 4 facility.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.42,0:19:56.81,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,However, his wounds are deep.\NWe’re not sure if he’ll survive.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.58,0:19:58.38,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I see…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.74,0:20:00.94,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,And about the ground\Nthat collapsed…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.14,0:20:04.34,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,There are traces of it being\Nmade to collapse that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.74,0:20:07.18,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Was there anything you noticed?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.58,0:20:15.50,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Is something wrong, you two?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.50,0:20:17.28,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh… That is…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.02,0:20:20.46,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,No, nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.98,0:20:24.15,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What? So strange of you two.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.38,0:20:30.61,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You! What are you going to do\Nabout my test Hollows?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.74,0:20:33.68,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Were those Hollows\Nfrom Squad 12?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.68,0:20:34.57,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.90,0:20:37.93,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems someone has\Nunlocked the testing facility
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.93,0:20:39.58,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,and had freed all the Hollows.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.94,0:20:43.05,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Who would do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.33,0:20:46.06,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,How should I know?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.42,0:20:47.31,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Nemu!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.31,0:20:49.78,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You weren’t watching carefully,\Nand this is what happened!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.78,0:20:51.18,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.58,0:20:53.86,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I’m sorry, Master Mayuri.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.18,0:20:56.53,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it,\NI’m really upset!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.94,0:20:59.30,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain of Squad 3!\NYou, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.30,0:21:01.14,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Why didn’t you try\Nto keep them alive?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.14,0:21:02.94,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I can’t do my tests now!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.94,0:21:04.99,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, now…\NDon’t get angry.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.14,0:21:19.89,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.62,0:21:22.16,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,There’s no one here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.10,0:21:25.80,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,A malfunction?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.23,0:23:23.14,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Abarai, why where you\Nwith Iba today?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.14,0:23:26.02,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,He forced me come with him\Nto discuss the future of
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.02,0:23:27.74,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,the Men's Soul Reaper\NAssociation.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.74,0:23:30.38,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,There’s no chance against the Women's\NSoul Reaper Association, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.38,0:23:31.12,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You’re so right.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.12,0:23:34.52,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s that kind of attitude\Nthat gets us ridiculed!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.23,0:23:36.55,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Illustrated Guide to Soul Reapers.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.00,0:23:40.20,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Byakuya, what is it that you\Nwanted to talk to me about?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.40,0:23:43.17,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo Kurosaki…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.58,0:23:46.10,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Itchy! I found you!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.33,0:23:48.31,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Yachiru,\Nwhat are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.43,0:23:53.08,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I fixed up Byakki’s house\Nand made a hidden tunnel.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.24,0:23:55.26,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I’ll show you too!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.26,0:23:58.18,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,– Okay, okay! Sorry, Byakuya.\N– Hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.18,0:24:02.38,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,How long do you intend to\Naddress me by my first name?